OL,5,Ccruelty
OL,7,FA mother who claims she did not know
OL,8,Fshe was pregnant until she gave birth
OL,9,Fhid her child from her family and
OL,10,Fpartner for almost three years -
OL,11,Fkeeping the youngster in a drawer
OL,12,Funder her bed.
OL,14,FThe mum, who cannot be named for legal
OL,15,Freasons, kept the little girl secret
OL,16,Ffor two years and 11 months, feeding
OL,17,Fher on a diet of Weetabix and water
OL,18,Fthrough a syringe and only letting her
OL,19,Fout when nobody else was around.
