OL,5,Ccruelty
OL,7,FDuring that time she continued to look
OL,8,Fafter her other children, taking them
OL,9,Fto and from school and celebrating
OL,10,Fbirthdays and Christmases.
OL,12,FThe girl - known as Child A - was
OL,13,Feventually discovered after the
OL,14,Fwoman's partner - who had been
OL,15,Fforbidden from going upstairs alone in
OL,16,Fthe Cheshire home - heard noises, and
OL,17,Fentered the bedroom.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/16
