OL,5,Ccruelty
OL,7,FDescribing what she did as "wicked
OL,8,Fbeyond belief" Honorary Recorder of
OL,9,FChester Judge Steven Everett jailed
OL,10,Fthe mother for seven and a half years
OL,11,Fafter she admitted child cruelty.
OL,13,FHe said: "To my mind what you did
OL,14,Ftotally defies belief.
OL,16,F"You starved that little girl of any
OL,17,Flove, any proper affection, any proper
OL,18,Fattention, any interaction with
OL,19,Fothers, a proper diet, much-needed
OL,20,Fmedical attention."
