OL,7,FHe added: "You attempted to control
OL,8,Fthis situation as carefully as you
OL,9,Fcould but by sheer chance your
OL,10,Fterrible secret was discovered.
OL,12,F"The consequences for (the child) were
OL,13,Fnothing short of catastrophic `
OL,14,Fphysically, psychologically and
OL,15,Fsocially."
OL,17,FThe youngster is now under the care of
OL,18,Ffoster parents - who said for the
OL,19,Ffirst few months they cared for her,
OL,20,Fshe never cried or asked for food or
OL,21,Fwater.
