OL,7,FChester Crown Court heard when she was
OL,8,Fdiscovered Child A was the size of a
OL,9,Feight-month-old, despite being just a
OL,10,Ffew weeks away from her third birthday.
OL,12,FHer hair was matted and she had dirty
OL,13,Fnails, she had a significant nappy
OL,14,Frash, swollen ankles and red limbs due
OL,15,Fto spending so much time in the divan
OL,16,Fbed drawer.
