OL,7,FChild A was born with a cleft lip and
OL,8,Fpalate but she did not seek medical
OL,9,Fassistance for her, nor was the child
OL,10,Fregistered.
OL,12,FThe court also heard during the
OL,13,Fmother's relationship with her
OL,14,Fboyfriend he was forbidden from going
OL,15,Fupstairs alone into her "safe space".
OL,17,FShe would also consistently play music
OL,18,For keep the television on in her
OL,19,Fbedroom, even when she was downstairs,
OL,20,Fto hide any noises coming from the
OL,21,Fchild.
