OL,7,FIn a police interview, the mother said
OL,8,Fthat when her boyfriend stayed round
OL,9,Fshe would put Child A in an empty
OL,10,Fbedroom.
OL,12,FShe also admitted she often left the
OL,13,Fchild alone in the house for long
OL,14,Fperiods of time, dropping her children
OL,15,Foff at school before going to work -
OL,16,Fleaving her on her own all day.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/16
