OL,7,FThe woman's partner told police on one
OL,8,Foccasion, on Christmas Eve, the mother
OL,9,Fand the other children went to his
OL,10,Fparent's house in the early morning,
OL,11,Fnot leaving until the evening of
OL,12,FChristmas Day - leaving Child A alone
OL,13,Fthe entire time.
OL,15,FThe secret was finally uncovered when
OL,16,Fthe mother rushed from the house to
OL,17,Ftake her other children to school.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/16
