OL,7,FAs her boyfriend was not allowed to be
OL,8,Fin the house alone he also went to
OL,9,Fleave, but feeling unwell, went back
OL,10,Fto use the bathroom, the court was
OL,11,Ftold.
OL,13,FAfter discovering the child he
OL,14,Fimmediately called the mother to
OL,15,Fconfront her about what he had seen,
OL,16,Fas well as his own mother who in
OL,17,Fturned called the parents of the
OL,18,Fdefendant.
