OL,7,FSenior Crown Prosecutor Rachel
OL,8,FWorthington, of CPS Mersey-Cheshire,
OL,9,Fsaid: "This child has been subjected
OL,10,Fto extreme neglect of her health,
OL,11,Fdevelopment, and basic care needs
OL,12,Fsince before she was born.
OL,14,F"She was left on her own for long
OL,15,Fperiods of time, sleeping in an
OL,16,Finappropriate and too small space, and
OL,17,Freceiving inadequate nutrition.
OL,19,F"When the mother went out with her
OL,20,Fother children or to work, the child
OL,21,Fwas simply left to fend for herself.
