OL,5,Ccruelty
OL,7,F"This child has never had a birthday
OL,8,Fpresent, a Christmas present or
OL,9,Fanything to recognise these days.
OL,10,FShe's had no interaction with any of
OL,11,Fher siblings.
OL,13,F"She hadn't known daylight or fresh
OL,14,Fair and didn't respond to her own name
OL,15,Fwhen she was first found.
