OL,5,Ccruelty
OL,7,F"This case has shocked all the
OL,8,Fprosecution team and has been very
OL,9,Fdifficult to work on. After reading
OL,10,Fthe evidence, I had to take myself
OL,11,Faway and try and process what I had
OL,12,Fread.
OL,14,F"I am a mother myself and simply
OL,15,Fcouldn't comprehend what this
OL,16,Fdefendant had done or why.
OL,18,F"The motive behind the mother's
OL,19,Fbehaviour is still not clear, but that
OL,20,Fis not the role of the Crown
OL,21,FProsecution Service.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUzD@AOU
