OL,7,F"Our job is to bring the person
OL,8,Fresponsible to justice. That has now
OL,9,Fbeen done and it is the profound hope
OL,10,Fof the CPS that the victim in this
OL,11,Fcase recovers sufficiently to live as
OL,12,Ffull a life as possible."
OL,14,FFollowing the sentencing DC Rachel Di
OL,15,FNicola said: "What this child has
OL,16,Fexperienced in its short lifetime is
OL,17,Fsimply unimaginable, and how anyone
OL,18,Fcan allow a child to suffer in that
OL,19,Fway is beyond belief.
