OL,7,F"The shocking neglect was on an
OL,8,Findescribable scale and the suffering
OL,9,Fthe child experienced will impact them
OL,10,Ffor the rest of their life.
OL,12,F"All those involved in the case have
OL,13,Fbeen left deeply shocked by what we
OL,14,Funcovered, and we have all been amazed
OL,15,Fby the way the child has recovered
OL,16,Fsince they were discovered, and we
OL,17,Fhope that this recovery continues ."
